Text: RE Heynsf Unfortunately I made other plans for the entire weekend before checking the calendar I wish I was going to be out of town a different weekend Are you going to Corvallis I will call you next time we are going to be in your part of town Eric and I wished we could have gone out last night but it was too late I know we are a losers Talk to you soon Original Message From mailto Sent Saturday November AM To Tcom Subject RE Hey Yeah I like to hassle Eric and I really kind of miss it actually My cell phone number is and my home number is I would love to grab a beer with ya sometime Are you going to the Civil War Game next weekend
